column25: 占位符，用于表示每一格对应的语言

column2: This is the moveable button, press shift+left mouse button to move\nClick the left mouse button again to determine the position\nRight mouse button to reset the position
column10: 这是可移动按钮，按shift+鼠标左键可以移动\n再点击一次鼠标左键确定位置\n鼠标右键重置位置
已添加到你的物品栏中

column2: This is the search box\nRight click to clear the text
column10: 这是搜索框，支持拼音搜索\n按下鼠标右键清空文本

column2: Enabling it will turn on fuzzy search
column10: 启用后将开启模糊搜索

column2: When enabled it will search for the spell ID instead of the name
column10: 启用后将搜索的是法术ID而不是名字

column2: has been removed from the favorites

Help
Ctrl+left click on a spell will put it directly into the inventory
Shift+left click on a spell will put it into the held wand
Alt+left click on a spell will put it into the favorite,
and if you perform this action in the favorite, you are deleting the spell from the favorite.
column10:
帮助
对一个法术按下ctrl+鼠标左键会直接放入背包
如果是shift+鼠标左键是放入手持法杖
对一个法术按下alt+鼠标左键会放入收藏中，
如果在收藏中执行此操作则是在收藏中删除此法术

column2: Click to fix the current wand and window
column10: 点击固定当前法杖和窗口

column2: Click to unfix the wand and window
column10: 点击取消固定法杖和窗口

column2:
Help:
Hold shift and left click on a grid to select
While holding shift down, left click on another grid to perform a box-select operation
Click on one side of the highlight box while holding shift to deselect it.
Ctrl+left click after selecting one or more squares allows you to move them.
Backspace to delete a spell
Hold down alt and left click to promote spell to Always Cast
column10:
帮助:
按住shift点击一个格子可以选择
按住shift的时候再点击另一个格子进行框选操作
按住shift的时候点击框选格的一边取消选择
选择了一个或多个格子之后按下ctrl键可以对其进行移动
退格键删除法术
按住alt键点击一个法术让其变成始终

column2: Shift+left click copy properties into the spawner\nleft click to copy the wand to the player's position
column10: 按住shift点击复制属性进生成器\n直接点击复制法杖到玩家位置

column2: Help\nAfter clicking on the highlight to select a wand \nHold the ctrl to click on another wand to swap positions
column10: 帮助\n在点击高亮选择了一个格子之后\n按下ctrl键点击另一个格子可以交换法杖位置

column2: The current box limit has been reached and no new wand can be added
column10: 当前仓库上限已达到，无法增加新法杖
加载选中法杖到自身位置

column2: Load selected wand into held wand
column10: 加载选中法杖替换掉当前手持法杖

column2: Sure you want to delete this page, it can't be recovered!
column10: 确定要删除此页面吗，删除后无法恢复！

column2: Holy shit, you managed to create 99,999 pages. Is your computer okay? You can't create any more pages.
column10: 我草，你居然能创建99999个页面，你电脑还好吗？你不能再创建新的页面了
